You're not seeing things.

446
00:31:50.541 --> 00:31:51.708
That him?

447
00:31:51.709 --> 00:31:53.443
That's him.

448
00:31:53.444 --> 00:31:56.313
We must shut this down.
How do we shut this down?

449
